page.title: 08A Typical Day
page.content: I get up and go down-stairs and have breakfast.I have time to play or read I get dressed at half past 7.Then I have a drink and have time to play.At 10 to 9 we get ready and go to school. I line up and we go in.We have the register then E.S. and French.At break I have an apple and run around .When the whistle goes we line up,go in and have Maths and House-craft.Then it's dinner time. After dinner we have music and English and then its home time.I get changed,get my bike and go and knock for a friend.At 5.30 I have tea. We have fish and chips.Then at 10 to 6 I go to youth club.We pay and I have a pound to spend.We buy a drink and sweets. Then its time to go swimming. We get in the pool at 8.00. When we get out we get dressed, go home, have a drink and go to bed.
